# Authentix - Production-Grade Content Intelligence System

## Phase 1: Architecture & Planning
- [x] Define system architecture
- [x] Create implementation plan
- [x] Get user approval

## Phase 2: Project Scaffold & Infrastructure
- [ ] Create monorepo structure
- [ ] Set up Docker Compose (PostgreSQL, Redis, Qdrant)
- [ ] Configure environment files and configs
- [ ] Set up CI/CD pipeline (GitHub Actions)

## Phase 3: API Gateway (Node.js / Fastify)
- [ ] Fastify server with JWT auth + rate limiting
- [ ] Route definitions: /analyze, /humanize, /full-report, /upload
- [ ] BullMQ job queue integration
- [ ] File upload handler (multipart)
- [ ] WebSocket / SSE for async job status

## Phase 4: Document Ingestion Service (Python)
- [ ] PDF parser (pdfplumber / pdfminer)
- [ ] DOCX parser (python-docx)
- [ ] Text normalizer (unicode, whitespace, section detection)
- [ ] Structured JSON output: {metadata, sections[], paragraphs[], tokens[]}
- [ ] Header/footer/watermark filtering

## Phase 5: Plagiarism Engine (Python / FastAPI)
- [ ] Shingling + MinHash + LSH exact matching
- [ ] Sentence embeddings (SBERT / E5)
- [ ] ANN search via Qdrant
- [ ] Structural comparison (paragraph alignment)
- [ ] Weighted hybrid score aggregation
- [ ] Source attribution with confidence scores

## Phase 6: AI Detection Engine (Python / FastAPI)
- [ ] RoBERTa/DeBERTa fine-tuned classifier
- [ ] Perplexity-based detector
- [ ] Stylometric feature extractor
- [ ] Calibrated ensemble meta-classifier
- [ ] Explainability: perplexity, burstiness, token uniformity, syntax entropy

## Phase 7: Humanization Engine (Python / FastAPI)
- [ ] Semantic structure parser
- [ ] Constrained rewrite pipeline (multiple candidates)
- [ ] Candidate ranker (semantic preservation + stylometric + AI-resistance)
- [ ] Validation firewall (entity lock, numeric fidelity, logical structure)
- [ ] Regeneration loop until validation passes

## Phase 8: Validation Engine (Python)
- [ ] SBERT semantic similarity (≥ 0.92 threshold)
- [ ] Named entity preservation checker (spaCy)
- [ ] Numerical consistency check
- [ ] Fact consistency validator

## Phase 9: Frontend (Next.js)
- [ ] Landing page with auth (sign in / sign up)
- [ ] Dashboard: upload file or paste text
- [ ] Results page: plagiarism report, AI score, humanized output
- [ ] Pill badges, highlight annotations, progress states
- [ ] Footer with "Made with love by Yaksh Bhesaniya"

## Phase 10: Evaluation & Observability
- [ ] Evaluation metrics service (AUC, calibration, precision/recall)
- [ ] Model drift monitoring
- [ ] False-positive tracking
- [ ] Rewrite rejection logging

## Phase 11: Deployment
- [ ] Dockerfiles for all services
- [ ] docker-compose.yml for local dev
- [ ] Load testing (k6 scripts)
